---
title: Hoisin-Glazed Duck Breast with Ginger-Garlic Rice & Crispy Shallots
description: Elegant and impressive yet without all the fuss! Beautifully glazed duck breast with baby broccoli and aromatic ginger-garlic rice
make for a fantastic special occasion dinner that's sure to make jaws drop the moment you serve up.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/hoisin-glazed-duck-breast-dbc228ff.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/hoisin-glazed-duck-breast-6169234bdfae7d00516b010f-cb766bde.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipes/hoisin-glazed-duck-breast-6169234bdfae7d00516b010f
